\#First read in the single csv file storing variables that are not
scored in VideoAnnotate's 1-9 scoring system, in this case nest score
(0-4 score for the quality of the nest at 30:00, Seconds to Initiate Pup
Retrieval, and Seconds to Complete Pup Retrieval, which are scored while
viewing the entire assay, rather than the 10-second chunks for random
scoring.

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\#check your working directory}
\FunctionTok{getwd}\NormalTok{()}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{verbatim}
## [1] "/Volumes/AIM1/Exemplar_R_Analysis_Folder/Behavior_Analysis_Files"
\end{verbatim}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\#you need to make sure this Rmd file is saved in same folder as the csv or txt files you try to read in/write. }

\NormalTok{WTMBT\_FULL\_ASSAY\_VARIABLES }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{read\_csv}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"FINAL\_VARIABLES\_TABLE.csv"}\NormalTok{, }
    \AttributeTok{col\_types =} \FunctionTok{cols}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{STRAIN =} \FunctionTok{col\_factor}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{levels =} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"DBA/2J"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"C57BL/6"}\NormalTok{)), }\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}}\AttributeTok{LACTATION DAY}\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{col\_factor}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{levels =} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"LD1"}\NormalTok{, }
        \StringTok{"LD3"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"LD5"}\NormalTok{)), }\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}}\AttributeTok{NEST SCORE}\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{col\_double}\NormalTok{(), }
        \AttributeTok{NOTES =} \FunctionTok{col\_skip}\NormalTok{()))}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{verbatim}

\end{verbatim}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\#To replace the "\_" in the Animal IDs with an "F" for "female"}
\NormalTok{WTMBT\_FULL\_ASSAY\_VARIABLES}\SpecialCharTok{$}\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}}\AttributeTok{ANIMAL ID}\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{gsub}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"\_"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"F"}\NormalTok{, WTMBT\_FULL\_ASSAY\_VARIABLES}\SpecialCharTok{$}\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}}\AttributeTok{ANIMAL ID}\StringTok{\textasciigrave{}}\NormalTok{)}

\CommentTok{\#To rename the ID/Strain/Day variables}
\FunctionTok{colnames}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_FULL\_ASSAY\_VARIABLES)}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"Full ID"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Strain"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Day"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Time at All Pups Retrieved"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Pup Retrieval Initiation (0{-}300)"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Pup Retrieval Initiation (0{-}1800)"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Nest Score"}\NormalTok{)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\CommentTok{\#Since each assay is stored as an individual txt file, this code compiles all the file names in a given folder to then use a loop for reading in each file:}

\NormalTok{file\_names }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{list.files}\NormalTok{(}\AttributeTok{pattern=}\StringTok{"*.txt"}\NormalTok{, }\AttributeTok{full.names=}\ConstantTok{TRUE}\NormalTok{)}

\FunctionTok{print}\NormalTok{(file\_names)}
\end{Highlighting}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\#this example filename format is Path/Path/Path/YYYYMMDD{-}CCCCC{-}SS{-}A{-}LLL where Y = year, M = month, D = day, C = Cohort ID, S = Strain ID (in most cases this would be experimental condition), A = Animal ID, L = Lactation Day (in most cases this would be experimental day \#)}

\CommentTok{\#now use a regular expression to extract that information into new columns}
\CommentTok{\# (?\textless{}Date\textgreater{}.*) denotes to capture the preceding information (?), label the column it\textquotesingle{}s captured in "Date" (\textless{} \textgreater{}), .* print whatever it is)}
\CommentTok{\# (?\textgreater{}{-}|\_) ?\textgreater{} means don\textquotesingle{}t capture the following hyphen or underscore}
\CommentTok{\# etc for the Cohort, Strain, Animal ID, Day}

\NormalTok{extracted\_file\_information}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\FunctionTok{data.frame}\NormalTok{(stringr}\SpecialCharTok{::}\FunctionTok{str\_match}\NormalTok{(split\_name,}\StringTok{"(?\textless{}Date\textgreater{}.*)(?\textgreater{}{-}|\_)(?\textless{}Cohort\textgreater{}.*)(?\textgreater{}{-}|\_)(?\textless{}Strain\textgreater{}B6|D2*)(?\textgreater{}{-}|\_)(?\textless{}Animal\textgreater{}.*)(?\textgreater{}{-}|\_)(?\textless{}Day\textgreater{}LD1|LD3|LD5*)$"}\NormalTok{))}
\FunctionTok{colnames}\NormalTok{(extracted\_file\_information)}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"FileName"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Date"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Cohort"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Strain"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Animal ID"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Day"}\NormalTok{)}

\CommentTok{\#just to see it}
\FunctionTok{print}\NormalTok{(extracted\_file\_information[}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{,])}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\#Transforming the dataset from individual rows for every event to event
counts in columns

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\#Transforming the dataset to be counts of event occurrences, rather than a row for every individual event}
\CommentTok{\#pulling out a list of every distinct Full.ID}
\NormalTok{individual\_names}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS }\SpecialCharTok{\%\textgreater{}\%} \FunctionTok{distinct}\NormalTok{(Full.IDs)}
\CommentTok{\#unlisting the result into a character vector}
\NormalTok{name\_vector}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\FunctionTok{unlist}\NormalTok{(individual\_names)}

\CommentTok{\#repeat for lactation days}
\NormalTok{lactation\_days}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS }\SpecialCharTok{\%\textgreater{}\%} \FunctionTok{distinct}\NormalTok{(Day)}
\NormalTok{days\_vector}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\FunctionTok{unlist}\NormalTok{(lactation\_days)}

\CommentTok{\#make an event code vector for the events scored in VideoAnnotate:}
\NormalTok{event\_codes}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{1}\SpecialCharTok{:}\DecValTok{9}\NormalTok{)}

                                                         
\CommentTok{\#For loop to transpose the row counts into event counts:}
\CommentTok{\#create empty data.frames:}
\NormalTok{WTMBT\_COMPLETE}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\FunctionTok{data.frame}\NormalTok{()}
\NormalTok{WTMBT\_transposed\_step}\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{data.frame}\NormalTok{()}
    
\CommentTok{\#Nested for loop to count for every distinct Full.ID, on every distinct Day, how many of each event (1{-}9) was scored for each animal:}
\ControlFlowTok{for}\NormalTok{(q }\ControlFlowTok{in}\NormalTok{ name\_vector)\{}
  \ControlFlowTok{for}\NormalTok{(r }\ControlFlowTok{in}\NormalTok{ days\_vector)\{}
    
\NormalTok{WTMBT\_transposed\_step }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{cbind}\NormalTok{(}
\StringTok{"Full ID"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{paste}\NormalTok{(q), }
\StringTok{"Day"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{paste}\NormalTok{(r),}
\StringTok{"Strain"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{paste}\NormalTok{(q),}
\StringTok{"Pups Retrieved and Grouped"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{)),}
\StringTok{"All Pups in Nest"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{)),}
\StringTok{"Pup Retrieval Event"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{3}\NormalTok{)),}
\StringTok{"Pup Interaction"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{4}\NormalTok{)),}
\StringTok{"Crouching Over Pups"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{5}\NormalTok{)),}
\StringTok{"Resting with Pups"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{6}\NormalTok{)),}
\StringTok{"Nest Building"} \OtherTok{=} \FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(}\FunctionTok{which}\NormalTok{(WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Full.IDs}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ q }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Day}\SpecialCharTok{==}\NormalTok{ r }\SpecialCharTok{\&}\NormalTok{ WTMBT\_PLUS\_FULLIDS}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{EventCodeNumber}\SpecialCharTok{==}\DecValTok{7}\NormalTok{)),}
